description:
Deadly Accusers of the Brethren - Satan is "the accuser of the brethren (Revelation 12:10), which means that he is constantly accusing and condemning the members and leaders of Gods Church. Sadly, he accuses through agents who do what he doesaccuse, accuse, accuse. We should beware of these agents, and avoid becoming accusers of the brethren ourselves. Many rationalize their accusatory spirit under the guise of being True Watchmen on the Walls of Zion. In this short video, Pastor Wohlberg offers seven practical ways to tell whether a person is a true watchman or a devilish accuser.
